metadata.name: AlbusDraco
metadata.description:
-AlbusDraco

The origin of the dragon is derived from Tiamat, the goddess of Mesopotamian mythology, and was worshiped by people as a divine being in the early days.

Regardless of all of above long history, We live in an era where dragons are consumed in movies, games and books than at any other time in history. But we just consume, we no longer appreciate.

This is my first dragon among nine other variations.

*First buyer will have limited Poster + AR
